# CatcherWall

This is the React.js frontend for Catcher.
It is hooked up to two backend service: [one for live updates](https://github.com/RubenPonce/pollerexplosionservice), and [one for general queries](https://github.com/RubenPonce/grahql-catcher).

## Intallation
```bash
npm i && npm start
```
localhost:3000

## Future Features
- More pages
- Live notifications with Browser API
- more section for main React app
